| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-7244 — Recovery Inhibition (rhysida)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 084a31e5-e7f9-54a4-9a41-e27ae6038146"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
